pr_title: Added Gitlab Authorization, changed task status registration methods & added gitlab contributor querying method in base worker class
pr_body:
Added a method for Gitlab API key authentication. It behaves similar to the Github authentication method and stores the API rate limit details available in the request header in oauth class variable. Also did minor changes in the task registration methods to incorporate task status updates from Gitlab worker.

Added a method to query gitlab contributors.

Resolves #749, #754 & #764

pr_body:
Adding gitlab-merge-request-worker with the following functionalities -

1. Query and store merge requests
2. Query and store MR labels
3. Query contributors (using worker_base)
4. Query MR events
5. Query MR comments/Notes

pr_body:
Complete Gitlab Merge Request Worker.
Queries following data-

- contributors
- pull_requests
- pull_request_assignees
- pull_request_events
- pull_request_labels
- pull_request_message_ref
- pull_request_meta
- pull_request_repo
- pull_request_reviewers
- pul_request_comments
- pull_request_commits
- pull_request_files
